    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1935-06-06T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1935-06-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="905"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d905">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">867.20/57</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Turkish Embassy</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Department of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Turkish General Staff is desirous to invite as instructor to the Army Air
                    School an experienced American General Staff Officer graduated from the Air
                    Academy and capable to teach Tactics and Organization in Air Forces.</p>
                <p>The Turkish Embassy would be much obliged to the State Department to intervene
                    with the competent Authorities for this matter.</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-06-06">June 6,
                            1935</date>.</dateline>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
